Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-ap806-dual.dtsi |    2 ++
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-ap806-quad.dtsi |    4 ++++
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/marvell/armada-ap806.dtsi      |    8 ++++++++
